groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:name: The King is Back.....here
groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:short_description: Not your typical bison tube in a pine tree.
groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:long_description:
The concept worked on paper. We'll see if it works for real. Look carefully and you should be able to figure it out. Stealth needed to get started. Pay attention to what you are doing so you can re-hide the container the same way. FTF gets a FTF pin and your own cache container to hide. Contains log, pencil and small swag.
Congratulations to JeepFeet for FTF.

groundspeak:log.groundspeak:text: Found it pretty quickly, but picked up a few all-natural souvenirs getting it. Found with dawnie22 and 19acassel.
